The inferomarginal illustrated here (
Fig. 8F
) is the holotype (
NHMM JJ 10490a
), while the other figured ossicles in lot NHMM JJ 10490 are paratypes. Additional material includes around 50 isolated ossicles (lot 
NHMM JJ 9591
). All material is from the upper Maastrichtian (Maastricht Formation, Emael Member, Lava Horizon) at the CBR-Romontbos Quarry, Eben Emael (Liège, northeast Belgium).
